      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Percy Powell. OF the Powell-San-\nders company, returned today from\nWashington city. where he went as\na member Of the Spokane commit\ntoe to urge the passage of the\n\"long haul, short haul' bill In con-\ngress.\n\n\nMr.. Powell said that he saw 81\ncongressman and nearly as many\nsenators. and feels very much en-.\ncouraged and thinks that the bill\nhas a fair chance to 60 through\nboth houses of congress. He found\nstrong sentiment in favor of the\nbill among the statesmen from the\nmiddle west and mountain states.\n\n\nMr.. Powell Is further very much\nencouraged over the prospect of a\nfavorable decision by the interstate\ncommerce commission, which will\npass on the Spokane rate case be-\ntween now and June Is."
    }
  ]
